Description of incident: Humana is notifying Wisconsin members of a breach of customers information after an  employee’s vehicle was broken into and a company laptop was  stolen along with a file containing customer information.  The information compromised included member names, dates of birth, Humana and clinic names. The documents also included Humana member identification numbers of 250 of those individuals.More information: http://www.wsaw.com/home/headlines/Laptop-with-Humana-member-information...
